5... Nxc3 6. dxc3 Be7
{ The most common move in online chess, and the second most played line in OTB chess, simply preparing ...O-O. }
7. Bf4 { Keeping the e5-pawn under protection and preparing O-O-O. } 7... O-O
8. O-O-O { Attacking the d5-pawn. } 8... c6
{ This is the most common way to deal with the pressure over the d5-pawn. } 9.
h4
{ The key idea to start the initiative! We are going to develop the initiative by playing Qg3, Nf3-Ng5 followed by Bd3 with a lot of pressure against black's king. }
