10... Nd5
{ Was played in an old Wesley So game. Here I suggest we go for the subtle: }
11. Qd2
{ Staying flexible, keeping both c4 and f4 in reserve for now.   11.c4  Was played by Wesley So, but Black got a reasonable position after:  11...Nde7∞  And the Knight went to f5 next with good control over the center. 1-0 So,W  (2531)  -Li,R  (2417)  Manila 2007 }
