{ Threatening to play Bg5! } 10... Ne7
{ With the idea to meet Bg5 with the creative ...Nexd5!?, giving up the Queen for active play. The good news is that there is no need to enter the complications, and you can play: }
11. h3
{ And the Knight lacks a good square to retreat. Also worth noting that: }
11... Nxd5 { Does not save Black because White has the important: } 12. hxg4
{ And suddenly Black is lost because of the Kingside pressure. } *

