d5 { Trying to open things up. } 14. Be3
{ Defending the Knight so we could play Qe1 next, chasing the enemy Queen. }
14... dxe4 15. Qe1
{ Offering a Queen trade because the endgames are close to winning for White thanks to the extra piece. }
15... Bh3+ 16. Ke2 { The King is surprisingly safe in the center! } 16... Qh5
17. Qg3
{ With a safe square for the King on f2, White will be able to enjoy the extra piece. }
