6... Nf6 7. Nge2
{ I find this move to be the most precise way of playing because it makes the ...Bg4 move less effective. }
7... Ng4 8. Ne4
{ Defending with tempo!   8.O-O ??  Is a common trap that you need to keep in mind and avoid  8...Qh4-+  And White is not able to defend the Kingside. }
