ning again to draw with Caruana at the 2016 Chess Olympiad at Baku.  @@HeaderStart@@Nowadays experts@@HeaderEnd@@ The biggest experts for the Black side of the Scandinavian that are implementing it regularly in their tournament practice in our time are:  - Grandmaster Sergey Tiviakov from the Netherlands @@StartBracket@@not only did he play the opening a lot, but he also wrote many articles about it, developing the theory@@EndBracket@@.  - Grandmaster Igor Kovalenko from Latvia. }
