{ Preparing either e5 and Ne4 or Nf1-Ng3 @@StartBracket@@the typical maneuver for the Ruy Lopez/Italian game@@EndBracket@@. }
9... d6 { Can be met by: } 10. Nf1 { Preparing Ng3. } 10... O-O 11. Ng3
{ We are ready to start asking some questions on the Queenside with b3. } *

